spec_data.Name: nodejs-burrito
spec_data.Description:
Burrito makes it easy to do crazy stuff with the JavaScript AST.

This is useful if you want to roll your own stack traces or build a code
coverage tool.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 02:05:01 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Wrap up expressions with a trace function while walking the AST
